{"type":null,"faqId":45287,"title":"4K 指的是什么？荣耀盒子M321的 4K 有什么特别之处吗？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.p1{margin-left:1.18125in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>4K 为超高清，分辨率为 3840 x 2160 像素，清晰度是 1080P（全高清，分辨率为 1920 x 1080 像素）的4倍。4K 视频会更清晰、更细腻、更逼真。如下图，不同分辨率下图片的清晰度。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>荣耀盒子M321特别之处在于采用了 H.265 的最新视频编码标准，相同的视频如果用H.265技术编码，比传统的H.264编码可以节省约50%的带宽。意味着，在网速相同的情况下，荣耀盒子M321播放 4K （高清、超清）视频比一般的盒子更流畅。是盒子类的真 4K 产品。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=164820\" style=\"width:4.375in;height:2.4270833in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":242,"faqType":"安装产品","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"808","faqTypeCode":"Media_Device-Setting-Up","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1442556870000,"seriesProductName":"MediaQ M321,MediaQ M321-20","visitedTimes":56,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"4K,特别,荣耀盒子","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}